{"tid":1838771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「派成績表」新鴻基：示威者行動得啖笑完全對商場業務無影響 上水廣場新年生意人流回升 商戶：生意忙到做到無停手","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T05:41:23.000Z","uid":252492,"like":9,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"67f6618bc254e4b0c606fda849602f82a5556452","tid":1838771,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"【香港零售】上水廣場生意「力保不失」 商戶：臨近新年人流回升做到無停手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2549067?=ez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2549067%3F%3Dez&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=283322de\" target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2549067?=ez</a><br />\n<br />\n hket<br />\n現在閱讀<br />\n【香港零售】上水廣場生意「力保不失」 商戶：臨近新年人流回升做到無停手<br />\n【香港零售】上水廣場生意「力保不失」 商戶：臨近新年人流回升做到無停手<br />\n 業界頭條 14:07 2020/01/23 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受社會事件影響，不少商場人流大減，但被視為「水貨客重鎮」的上水廣場人流未有因此而減少，相反臨近農曆新年人流特別多。有商戶指，最近幾日做到「無停手」，預計生意跟去年相若。<br />\n<br />\n人流未有太大影響 近日做到無停手<br />\n<br />\n在上水廣場不時會見到「拖喼客」，甚至會見到他們在店舖門口整理貨品，商場內亦有不少大品牌進駐。在商場內售賣運動鞋的劉小姐指，近幾個月商場的人流沒有太大影響，「除了示威那幾天」，而臨近農曆新年不論是內地客還是本地客都到店舖購物，劉小姐更指最近幾日做到「無停手」，預期生意跟去年同期相若。"},{"pid":"7fa3acd07fba44cdcb06744ddf807dcb17dae5d8","tid":1838771,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"小租戶批新地：佢哋喺地球上消失咗<br />\n不過，業主與商戶共渡時艱，卻非必然的事。陳與其代表食肆，於過去數月不斷與新地及九倉就減租不停交涉，「佢嘅租務部都會叫我去寫信，但係通常得返嚟嘅回覆都係話冇，尤其是新鴻基，話一毫子都唔會減，而家直頭喺地球上消失咗。」至於九倉，上月有報道指有商戶經磋商多時，終獲減租約半年，減幅約15%至20%，「我就冇受惠嘅，但我知嘅係如果租約就完，呢幾個月減租就會易傾啲。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200108/60460858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60460858&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=40399c5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60460858&h=0767717d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200108/60460858</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lhe9fBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhe9fBn.png&h=1db55097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7Exdn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7Exdn8.png&h=ca414f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61fTHgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61fTHgx.png&h=640ac13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n信和：依幾個月有出通告話商場唔開既日子先賠租 中間2 3點有示威或防暴商場落閘逼商戶關門趕顧客走既日子全部唔賠<br />\n<br />\n新地：近排已經攪左好多會員推廣吸引人流 唔會減租或免租 之前落閘既日子都唔會賠<br />\n<br />\n10月同11月好多大商場都有好多非大連鎖店既細鋪已經執鳩哂<br />\n可以留意下大商場d冷行已經變哂吉鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大地產商回應商場租戶 話近日社會已經回復平靜 已經無哂周圍破壞同蹤火 商場集會阻礙營業 唔會減租或免租共渡時艱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778223\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c47c582a3fc3566a705373d65d327bb236f7b0b7","tid":1838771,"uid":44358,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"手足攪唔掂，就武漢肺炎出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時辰到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a346db2eabfd93452e77270e760bfaff58c56e","tid":1838771,"uid":21920,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"係囉係囉<br />\n隻肺炎咁勁<br />\n示威唔洗搵名搏"},{"pid":"ea50cbb1e01ddf3612b34c7c6ee378201e0ee33e","tid":1838771,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8a56e79a4a844a8e2b608f74c4f19f39e15a54db","tid":1838771,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a49e4f50410f3989526b297404ad92ad0260f2","tid":1838771,"uid":36065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"好彩灑水無人搞咋"},{"pid":"3e7ba4cfa3fd80fc4eb1418fd7c4ab827d6a5b31","tid":1838771,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6185c78abada17657e38a646cbf1177f1de89374","tid":1838771,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"光復上水踢gip真係本重利少<br />\n用番中共慣用既白色恐怖先係治本"},{"pid":"2a16b931220782dd39d88fa91038a40a4795af7a","tid":1838771,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba7263bb0efee5d409c1b70b499a98a1f22914a","tid":1838771,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca7a6bfd05eeceecf86709eb70b2a6625666c4c8","tid":1838771,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"你話係咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db46492ed705337085ac38f4f0547927c0d92669","tid":1838771,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"特首已流亡海外?? 疫情失控, 港人自救有辦法??<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838790\" data-auto-link 